  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA14">
<l>paṇṭip perumpatiyai yākkip paḻipāvaṅ</l>
<l>koṇṭiṅku vāḻvāraik kūṟātē – yeṇṭicaiyum</l>
<l>pērttakara nāṉkuṭaiyāṉ pērōtip pētaikā</l>
<l>ṭīrttakara rāmiṉ ṟirintu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Without talking to those who live here with guilt [and] sin,</l>
<l>making [their] bellies great places, o foolish people, reciting the names</l>
<l>of the one possessing four arms that stretch to  all eight directions,</l>
<l>turn [to him and] make yourselves pure.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
